  "text": "After performing a quantization hyperparameter design exploration we conducted the quantized training of the use case NN using both the standard STE approach in TensorFlow library [CITATION_1] and the proposed scheme. It is to be noted that TensorFlow's scheme does not quantize the bias. This means that, when mapped to the crossbars, additional quantization studies would be needed.",
